	<h2><span><span class="conr">#1&nbsp;</span><a href="viewtopic.php?pid=33#p33">2008-03-04 13:13:30</a></span></h2>
	<div class="box">
		<div class="inbox">
			<div class="postleft">
				<dl>
					<dt><strong><a href="profile.php?id=89601">dave</a></strong></dt>
					<dd class="usertitle"><strong>Editor</strong></dd>
					<dd class="postavatar"></dd>
				</dl>
			</div>
			<div class="postright">
				<h3>Discussion of BEP 7: IPv6 Tracker Extension</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>The IPv6 tracker extension is being tested in the BitTorrent, Inc. trackers.&nbsp; We call for other tracker implementers to prototype this extension in order to gain experience with it.&nbsp; If you find any deficiencies in the proposal then please point it out here.<br /><br />See <a href="http://www.bittorrent.org/beps/bep_0007.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.bittorrent.org/beps/bep_0007.html</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="clearer"></div>
